metadata.name: Screaming Girl #001
metadata.description:
“Beautiful, colourful, radiant, yet grotesque and somewhat humorous, providing the viewer with an instant dopamine hit of hyper reality.”

Screaming Girl smiles as she trudges through the blackness. But, is it a grin, or a grimace? Is it a distant echo, or a dim roar? Awkward as an alien pretending to be human for social acceptance. Whispers from another dimension, Demons & Angels battling for her soul. Hovering somewhere between good and evil. Her soul is for sale, but who will buy it?

Sakura Mori is Born in Japan. Lives and works in London.

・Every piece is unique 1/1
